  "description": "How to Standardize Transcript Interpretation Across Staff: a practical workflow for tax professionals, including what to do, what to avoid, and a CTA to generate a transcript report.",
  "content": "<section>\n        <h2 id=\"goal\" class=\"section-heading\">What This Workflow Solves</h2>\n        <p class=\"article-text\">This is a repeatable workflow for tax professionals who want faster transcript reviews and cleaner client communication. It’s designed for consistency across staff, not “hero mode.”</p>\n       </section>\n       <section>\n        <h2 id=\"steps\" class=\"section-heading\">Workflow Steps</h2>\n        <div class=\"card-glass card-hover p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700\">\n        <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-sm\">\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Build the timeline (posted dates and key milestones).</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Confirm the transcript type and the tax period.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Deliver next steps with a clear action/no-action split.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Flag holds, notices, and balance signals.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"/></svg><span>Translate codes into client language (one narrative, not a glossary).</span></li>\n        </ul>\n        </div>\n       </section>\n       <section>\n        <h2 id=\"pitfalls\" class=\"section-heading\">Common Pitfalls</h2>\n        <div class=\"card-glass p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-700\">\n         <h3 class=\"font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Common pitfalls</h3>\n         <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-slate-300 text-sm\">\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Letting the client steer the review with a single code they Googled.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Mixing multiple years and transcript types in one narrative.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Overpromising on IRS timelines or outcomes.</span></li>\n<li class=\"flex gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4 text-rose-300 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.29 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0Z\"/></svg><span>Skipping documentation (what you checked, what you concluded, why).</span></li>\n         </ul>\n        </div>\n       </section>\n       <section>\n        <h2 id=\"cta-parser\" class=\"section-heading\">Turn Findings Into a Deliverable</h2>\n        <p class=\"article-text\">The fastest way to standardize staff output is to standardize the deliverable. Generate a report that matches your workflow, every time.</p>\n        <div class=\"mt-6\">\n         <a href=\"/#how-it-works\" class=\"btn-primary text-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center\">Parse Transcript Now</a>\n        </div>\n       </section>",
